	* [r4796] src/commands.c: CmdXfrBlockCHAR_T0(): limit the received
	  length to 0x1000 for ICCD Version A length is 16-bits and
	  usb_control_msg() fails with "Invalid argument" if the length is
	  > 0x100
	  
