	* [r2355] INSTALL: document how to use --enable-udev on FreeBSD.
	  
	  Thanks to Tilman Linneweh

2007-01-20  Ludovic Rousseau

	* [r2351] README: version 1.2.0 was released in 2007 not 2006 :-)

